data.description: Welcome home to your charming new home just steps from Slidell High. This large four bedroom, two bath home is situated perfectly on an expansive corner lot. Bring your personal touch to make it uniquely yours. Priced to sell quickly – seize this opportunity! This great neighborhood offers endless possibilities. Easy access to Old Town Slidell, Fremaux Town Center, Slidell Memorial Hospital and Gause Blvd. Forty minutes to downtown New Orleans makes for an easy commute. Top-rated school district. Schedule your showing today!
